{
  "video_id": "PfWGiu0jGv0",
  "title": "How we can help hungry kids, one text at a time | Su Kahumbu",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12720.0,
      "end_time": 15200.0,
      "text": "I want to introduce you to my badass friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16790.0,
      "end_time": 17680.0,
      "text": "Meet Thelma and Louise."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18240.0,
      "end_time": 20134.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20160.0,
      "end_time": 22160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m passionate about cows."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22400.0,
      "end_time": 24616.0,
      "text": "And although they&#39;ve been getting a lot of crap lately"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24640.0,
      "end_time": 27160.0,
      "text": "due to methane emissions and climate change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27400.0,
      "end_time": 29816.0,
      "text": "I hope that I can redeem their reputation in part"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29840.0,
      "end_time": 32950.0,
      "text": "by showing you how incredibly important they are"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32119.0,
      "end_time": 35215.0,
      "text": "in solving one of the world&#39;s biggest problems: food security."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35240.0,
      "end_time": 37416.0,
      "text": "But more importantly, for Africa --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37440.0,
      "end_time": 39480.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s resultant childhood stunting."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40920.0,
      "end_time": 43336.0,
      "text": "Nutritional stunting manifests itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43360.0,
      "end_time": 46216.0,
      "text": "in a reduction of growth rate in human development."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46240.0,
      "end_time": 48176.0,
      "text": "And according to UNICEF,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48200.0,
      "end_time": 49816.0,
      "text": "stunting doesn&#39;t come easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49840.0,
      "end_time": 51456.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t come quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51480.0,
      "end_time": 53296.0,
      "text": "It happens over a long period of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53320.0,
      "end_time": 56800.0,
      "text": "during which a child endures painful and debilitating cycles of illness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57600.0,
      "end_time": 59336.0,
      "text": "depressed appetite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59360.0,
      "end_time": 60936.0,
      "text": "insufficient nutrition"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60960.0,
      "end_time": 62560.0,
      "text": "and inadequate care."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63800.0,
      "end_time": 66000.0,
      "text": "And most kids simply can&#39;t endure such rigors."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66760.0,
      "end_time": 68360.0,
      "text": "But those that do survive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70000.0,
      "end_time": 72976.0,
      "text": "they carry forward long-term cognitive problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73000.0,
      "end_time": 75120.0,
      "text": "as well as losses of stature."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76840.0,
      "end_time": 80856.0,
      "text": "The numbers of stunted children under the age of five,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80880.0,
      "end_time": 82336.0,
      "text": "in most regions of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82360.0,
      "end_time": 83896.0,
      "text": "has been declining."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83920.0,
      "end_time": 85936.0,
      "text": "And I really hate to say this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85960.0,
      "end_time": 88856.0,
      "text": "but the only place where they haven&#39;t been declining is here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88880.0,
      "end_time": 90800.0,
      "text": "in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90960.0,
      "end_time": 93559.0,
      "text": "Here, 59 million children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94520.0,
      "end_time": 96655.0,
      "text": "three in 10 in that age group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96680.0,
      "end_time": 99536.0,
      "text": "struggle to meet their genetic potential --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 99560.0,
      "end_time": 101120.0,
      "text": "their full genetic potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103240.0,
      "end_time": 106735.0,
      "text": "Protein is one of our most important dietary requirements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 106760.0,
      "end_time": 109776.0,
      "text": "and evidence shows that lack of essential amino acids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109800.0,
      "end_time": 112576.0,
      "text": "the building blocks of proteins, in young children&#39;s diets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 112600.0,
      "end_time": 113839.0,
      "text": "can result in stunting."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114560.0,
      "end_time": 116576.0,
      "text": "Essential amino acids are called essential"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116600.0,
      "end_time": 119136.0,
      "text": "because we can&#39;t synthesize them in our bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119160.0,
      "end_time": 120840.0,
      "text": "We have to get them from our foods"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121560.0,
      "end_time": 124616.0,
      "text": "and the best sources are animal-derived:"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124640.0,
      "end_time": 126960.0,
      "text": "milk, meat and eggs."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127640.0,
      "end_time": 132160.0,
      "text": "Most protein consumed on the African continent is crop-based."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 135920.0,
      "text": "And although we have millions of smallholder farmers rearing animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 136880.0,
      "end_time": 140160.0,
      "text": "livestock production is not as easy as we think."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140960.0,
      "end_time": 144896.0,
      "text": "The big livestock gaps between rich countries and poor countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144920.0,
      "end_time": 146440.0,
      "text": "are due to poor animal health."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147640.0,
      "end_time": 150136.0,
      "text": "Endemic livestock diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150160.0,
      "end_time": 152536.0,
      "text": "some of them transmissible to humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152560.0,
      "end_time": 156560.0,
      "text": "threaten not only livestock producers in those poor countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157600.0,
      "end_time": 161519.0,
      "text": "but all human health across all countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162800.0,
      "end_time": 164576.0,
      "text": "This is a global pathogens network."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164600.0,
      "end_time": 167960.0,
      "text": "It shows the pathogens found across the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167120.0,
      "end_time": 170496.0,
      "text": "according to the Enhanced Infectious Diseases database."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 170520.0,
      "end_time": 174256.0,
      "text": "And it shows those pathogens that share hosts."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174280.0,
      "end_time": 175576.0,
      "text": "In a nutshell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175600.0,
      "end_time": 178550.0,
      "text": "we share pathogens, and thus diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178800.0,
      "end_time": 180496.0,
      "text": "with the species we live closest to:"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180520.0,
      "end_time": 181776.0,
      "text": "our livestock."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181800.0,
      "end_time": 184560.0,
      "text": "And we call these zoonotic diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184800.0,
      "end_time": 185856.0,
      "text": "Recent reports show"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 185880.0,
      "end_time": 189936.0,
      "text": "that the deadly dozen zoonotic diseases kill 2.2 million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189960.0,
      "end_time": 192960.0,
      "text": "and sicken 2.4 billion people annually."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193600.0,
      "end_time": 194856.0,
      "text": "And Jimmy says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 194880.0,
      "end_time": 197335.0,
      "text": "\"The greatest burden of zoonoses"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 197360.0,
      "end_time": 199920.0,
      "text": "falls on one billion poor livestock keepers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 200880.0,
      "end_time": 204600.0,
      "text": "We totally underestimate the importance of our smallholder farmers."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 205200.0,
      "end_time": 207616.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re beginning to recognize how important they are"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 207640.0,
      "end_time": 211136.0,
      "text": "and how they influence our medical health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 211160.0,
      "end_time": 212896.0,
      "text": "our biosafety"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 212920.0,
      "end_time": 216119.0,
      "text": "and more recently, our cognitive and our physical health."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217320.0,
      "end_time": 220680.0,
      "text": "They stand at the frontline of zoonotic epidemics."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 222480.0,
      "end_time": 224760.0,
      "text": "They pretty much underpin our existence."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 225880.0,
      "end_time": 228816.0,
      "text": "And they need to know so much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228840.0,
      "end_time": 233256.0,
      "text": "yet most lack knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 233280.0,
      "end_time": 236160.0,
      "text": "on livestock disease prevention and treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 236400.0,
      "end_time": 238176.0,
      "text": "So how do they learn?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 238200.0,
      "end_time": 240976.0,
      "text": "Apart from shared experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 241000.0,
      "end_time": 242256.0,
      "text": "trial and error,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 242280.0,
      "end_time": 246400.0,
      "text": "conventional farming extension services are boots on the ground and radio --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 247520.0,
      "end_time": 251800.0,
      "text": "expensive and hard to scale in the face of population growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 252880.0,
      "end_time": 254480.0,
      "text": "Sounds pretty gloomy, doesn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 255720.0,
      "end_time": 258495.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re at an interesting point in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 258519.0,
      "end_time": 262856.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re changing that narrative using innovative solutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 262880.0,
      "end_time": 265320.0,
      "text": "riding across scalable technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 266360.0,
      "end_time": 268640.0,
      "text": "Knowledge doesn&#39;t have to be expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 269560.0,
      "end_time": 273896.0,
      "text": "My company developed an agricultural platform called iCow."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 273920.0,
      "end_time": 277976.0,
      "text": "We teach farmers best livestock practices using SMS"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 278000.0,
      "end_time": 280336.0,
      "text": "over simple, low-end phones."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 280360.0,
      "end_time": 283616.0,
      "text": "Farmers receive three SMSs a week on best livestock practices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 283640.0,
      "end_time": 287776.0,
      "text": "and those that execute the messages go on to see increases in productivity"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 287800.0,
      "end_time": 290960.0,
      "text": "within as short a time as three months."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 292680.0,
      "end_time": 297840.0,
      "text": "The first increases in productivity, of course, are improved animal health."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 299000.0,
      "end_time": 301336.0,
      "text": "We use SMS because it is retentive."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 301360.0,
      "end_time": 303136.0,
      "text": "Farmers store their messages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 303160.0,
      "end_time": 304696.0,
      "text": "they write them down in books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 304720.0,
      "end_time": 305976.0,
      "text": "and in effect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 306000.0,
      "end_time": 308760.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re drip-feeding agricultural manuals into the fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 310440.0,
      "end_time": 316896.0,
      "text": "We recognize that we are all part of the global food network:"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 316920.0,
      "end_time": 318736.0,
      "text": "producers and consumers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 318760.0,
      "end_time": 320880.0,
      "text": "you and me, and every farmer."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 322440.0,
      "end_time": 327400.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re focusing now on trying to bring together producers and consumers"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 328400.0,
      "end_time": 333575.0,
      "text": "to take action and take responsibility for not only food security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 333600.0,
      "end_time": 335400.0,
      "text": "but for food safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 335840.0,
      "end_time": 341215.0,
      "text": "This beautiful animal is an African-Asian Sahiwal crossed with a Dutch Fleckvieh."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 341240.0,
      "end_time": 343656.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s milkier than her Sahiwal mom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 343680.0,
      "end_time": 348000.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s sturdier and more resistant to disease than her Fleckvieh father."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 349000.0,
      "end_time": 351960.0,
      "text": "In Ethiopia and Tanzania,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 351120.0,
      "end_time": 357560.0,
      "text": "the African Dairy Genetic Gains program is using SMS and cutting-edge genomics"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 357800.0,
      "end_time": 362536.0,
      "text": "and pioneering Africa&#39;s first tropically adapted dairy breeding centers"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 362560.0,
      "end_time": 365760.0,
      "text": "and dairy performance recording centers."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 366680.0,
      "end_time": 369816.0,
      "text": "Farmers contribute their production data --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 369840.0,
      "end_time": 371950.0,
      "text": "milking records,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 371120.0,
      "end_time": 373160.0,
      "text": "breeding records and feeding records --"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 373400.0,
      "end_time": 374776.0,
      "text": "to the ADGG platform."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 374800.0,
      "end_time": 376936.0,
      "text": "This stage is synthesized through algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 376960.0,
      "end_time": 380496.0,
      "text": "from some of the top livestock institutions in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 380520.0,
      "end_time": 383296.0,
      "text": "before it lands back in the farmers&#39; hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 383320.0,
      "end_time": 385440.0,
      "text": "in actionable SMSs."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 386520.0,
      "end_time": 387736.0,
      "text": "Customized data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 387760.0,
      "end_time": 389336.0,
      "text": "customized responses"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 389360.0,
      "end_time": 392160.0,
      "text": "all aimed at increasing productivity"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 392400.0,
      "end_time": 393960.0,
      "text": "based on the potential on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 394960.0,
      "end_time": 398159.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re at a very interesting place in agriculture in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 398920.0,
      "end_time": 400176.0,
      "text": "By the end of this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 400200.0,
      "end_time": 403440.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll have almost one billion mobile phone subscriptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 404400.0,
      "end_time": 406616.0,
      "text": "We have the power in our hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 406640.0,
      "end_time": 410895.0,
      "text": "to ensure that livestock production systems are not only healthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 410920.0,
      "end_time": 412920.0,
      "text": "productive and profitable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 413600.0,
      "end_time": 415936.0,
      "text": "but that farmers are knowledgeable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 415960.0,
      "end_time": 417775.0,
      "text": "and more importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 417800.0,
      "end_time": 419680.0,
      "text": "that our farmers are safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 420440.0,
      "end_time": 422160.0,
      "text": "Working with smallholder farmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 422400.0,
      "end_time": 425400.0,
      "text": "is one of the best ways to guarantee food security."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 426160.0,
      "end_time": 428816.0,
      "text": "Working with smallholder farmers is one of the best ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 428840.0,
